Name: Good Goods Incorporated
About the game: Good Goods Incorporated is a cute logistics tycoon game set on Earth. You're the CEO of a small company that buy and sells goods. Your goal is to make a lot of money! Trade steel, food, gold and water and ship them around to meet supply and demand. Features 1+ hrs of playtime Use boats, airplanes and delivery vans to ship your goods all around the world Start on a different place on Earth every time, every playthrough is different!
